dataset.description: Non-Critical Access Hospitals (CAHs) with swing beds are hospitals that provide Medicare Part A Skilled Nursing Facility (SNF) services to beneficiaries and must report data on certain measures of quality to Medicare through the Skilled Nursing Facility Quality Reporting Program (SNF QRP). This file contains a list of the swing bed units participating in the SNF QRP, as well as their results on quality measures implemented under the IMPACT Act.
dataset.title: Skilled Nursing Facility Quality Reporting Program – Swing Beds – Provider Data

theme.title: Skilled nursing facilities and nursing homes
